   "source": [
    "说明：\n",
    "    给定一个整数 (32 位有符号整数)，请编写一个函数来判断它是否是 4 的幂次方。\n",
    "\n",
    "示例 1:\n",
    "    输入: 16\n",
    "    输出: true\n",
    "\n",
    "示例 2:\n",
    "    输入: 5\n",
    "    输出: false\n",
    "\n",
    "进阶：\n",
    "    你能不使用循环或者递归来完成本题吗？"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "class Solution:\n",
    "    def isPowerOfFour(self, num: int) -> bool:\n",
    "        return num > 0 and num & (num-1) == 0 and num % 3 == 1"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "False"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 4,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "solution = Solution()\n",
    "solution.isPowerOfFour(5)"
   ]
  },
